information: Itac Professional, Importaco’s B2B brand for the food industry, is a leading supplier of nuts for companies of the food industry who strive to stay up-to-date with the latest trends and to innovate by incorporating nuts into their processes. Our wide selection of products allows us to supply these industries with almonds –processed at a Peanut-Free factory-, peanuts and other ingredients in different formats, ranging from pastes to dices, flakes and slices. We specialise in almonds and peanuts and we take care even of the slightest detail in their processing, from the moment they are harvested in the field and processed in the factory, until they are delivered to our clients based on their needs. Furthermore, we can offer specific solutions for each food industry segment: chocolates, baked goods, confectionery, diary products and ice creams, among others. Visit our website for more information.
